425
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:04,120
So you see Lorentz transformations are really quite simple.

426
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:06,120
They're stretching along one axis.

427
00:20:06,120 --> 00:20:08,120
And squeezing along the other axis.

428
00:20:08,120 --> 00:20:11,120
But they preserve the 45 degree axes.

429
00:20:11,120 --> 00:20:15,120
They don't preserve other lines in here.

430
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:17,120
Other lines will get stretched this way.

431
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:19,120
And squeeze the other direction.

432
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:21,620
But the ones which are along

433
00:20:21,620 --> 00:20:24,120
