434
00:20:24,120 --> 00:20:26,120
So that's the nature of Lorentz transformations.

435
00:20:26,120 --> 00:20:31,120
Sort of a squashing of one light-like direction.

436
00:20:31,120 --> 00:20:34,120
An expansion of the other light-like direction.

437
00:20:34,120 --> 00:20:35,120
Along.

